OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FAs the US and Israel's war with Iran
OL,7,Fsqueezes global oil supplies, there
OL,8,Fare fears about the cost and
OL,9,Favailability of flights as travellers
OL,10,Fplan their late spring and summer
OL,11,Ftrips.
OL,13,FThe head of the International Energy
OL,14,FAgency has warned that European
OL,15,Fcountries could run low on jet fuel
OL,16,Fwithin weeks, forcing the continent's
OL,17,Fairlines and carriers that fly to
OL,18,FEurope to significantly reduce flights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
