OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777097137
OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThe UK government recently issued a
OL,7,Fstatement urging people not to worry
OL,8,For change their plans, but they also
OL,9,Fsaid they were working with airlines
OL,10,Fand airports to plan for possible
OL,11,Fshortages.
OL,13,FMany airlines have already raised
OL,14,Fchecked bag fees or added fuel
OL,15,Fsurcharges as the global price of jet
OL,16,Ffuel increased from about $99 (#73.31)
OL,17,Fper barrel at the end of February to
OL,18,Fas high as $209 (#154.76) a barrel at
OL,19,Fthe beginning of April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
