OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FSo are flight tickets going up, and
OL,7,Fare flights being cancelled? ITV News
OL,8,Fhas contacted a number of airlines to
OL,9,Ffind out.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAir France / KLM
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
