OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FAir France and KLM have increased
OL,7,Fticket prices. For Economy Class
OL,8,Ftickets on long-haul flights, the fare
OL,9,Fincrease is E100 (#86.81) per round
OL,10,Ftrip.
OL,12,FFor flights to the United States,
OL,13,FCanada, and Mexico, the increase is
OL,14,FE70 (#60.77) per round trip. For short-
OL,15,F and medium-haul Economy Class
OL,16,Fflights, the increase is E10 (#8.68)
OL,17,Fper round trip.
OL,26,@qD@MOkvD@AOkxD@ZOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
