OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777097137
OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FStarting from April 27, KLM will
OL,7,Foperate 80 fewer round-trip flights in
OL,8,Fthe coming month due to rising jet
OL,9,Ffuel costs.
OL,11,FThis represents less than 1% of their
OL,12,Fflights within Europe during that time
OL,13,Fand passengers booked on these flights
OL,14,Fwill be rebooked onto the next
OL,15,Favailable flight.
OL,17,FThey told us they are actively
OL,18,Fmonitoring fuel supply as it affects
OL,19,Fall airlines but there is no
OL,20,Fdisruption at the moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
