PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777097137
OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The airline will
OL,7,Fwork with its suppliers to secure the
OL,8,Fjet fuel available in line with its
OL,9,Fneeds.
OL,11,F"We'll keep customers informed and
OL,12,Fprovide timely updates if needed."
OL,14,F20,000 short-haul flights will be
OL,15,Fremoved from the schedule through
OL,16,FOctober due to the price of jet fuel
OL,17,Fwhich has doubled since the outbreak
OL,18,Fof the Iran conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
