OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThey say the first 120 daily flight
OL,7,Fcancellations were implemented on
OL,8,FMonday (20 April), effective through
OL,9,Fthe end of May, and affected
OL,10,Fpassengers have been notified.
OL,12,FFor the flights scheduled in the
OL,13,Fsummer timetable, Lufthansa expects a
OL,14,Flargely stable fuel supply.
OL,16,FAll Lufthansa Group airlines will
OL,17,Fsuspend flights to the Middle East
OL,18,Fthrough April 30.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
