OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThey say ticket prices may continue to
OL,7,Fincrease due to the current
OL,8,Fgeopolitical environment.
OL,10,FITV News understands they are
OL,11,Fcurrently seeing no disruption to
OL,12,Fflights and don't plan to make any
OL,13,Fchanges to their flying schedule.
OL,15,FVirgin Atlantic
OL,17,FThe fuel surcharge for each cabin is
OL,18,Fas follows:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
