OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FITV News understands there is no
OL,7,Fimmediate risk to supply on their
OL,8,Froutes at present, with flights
OL,9,Foperating as normal.
OL,11,FFly Emirates
OL,13,FThey say they are currently operating
OL,14,Fa reduced number of flights until
OL,15,Ffurther notice.
OL,17,FQatar Airways
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
