OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThey say they are expanding their
OL,7,Finternational flight network, with
OL,8,Fservices to over 150 destinations from
OL,9,FJune.
OL,11,FTheir new schedule, valid until mid-
OL,12,FSeptember, introduces new routes and
OL,13,Fincreased frequencies to and from Doha.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the company told
OL,16,Fus: "It will depend on how the
OL,17,Fsituation evolves; as of now, we are
OL,18,Foperating normally."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
