OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FITV News has also contacted Airlines
OL,7,FUK, International Airlines Group,
OL,8,FRyanair, Air India and American
OL,9,FAirlines but they are yet to comment
OL,10,Fon this.
OL,12,FWhat should you do if your flight is
OL,13,Fcancelled?
OL,15,FUnder UK law, if your flight is
OL,16,Fcancelled, you are entitled to a full
OL,17,Frefund or a spot on an alternative
OL,18,Fflight that is reasonable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
