OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThis applies to customers flying from
OL,7,Fa UK airport, arriving in the country
OL,8,Fon a European Union (EU) or UK
OL,9,Fairline, or arriving at an EU airport
OL,10,Fon a UK airline.
OL,12,FIf your flight is delayed, the airline
OL,13,Fmust provide a reasonable amount of
OL,14,Ffood and drink.
OL,16,FAirlines are required to pay
OL,17,Fcompensation if flights arrive more
OL,18,Fthan three hours late, but only when
OL,19,Fit is deemed to be within their
OL,20,Fcontrol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
