OL,3,CWhich airlines are cancelling flights
OL,4,Cand pushing up prices?
OL,6,FThe UK government said on April 24
OL,7,Fthat there was currently no shortage
OL,8,Fof jet fuel in the UK and was not
OL,9,Fadvising people to change their travel
OL,10,Fplans.
